│ The test failures indicate that my fix is too restrictive. The issue is that I'm requiring `nuw` flags for all equality comparisons, but there are legitimate cases where the             │
│ optimization should still apply even without explicit `nuw` flags.                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                           │
│ Looking at the failing tests, particularly `compare-alloca.ll`, I see that the test expects:                                                                                              │
│ ```llvm                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ %g = getelementptr i8, ptr %m, i32 %offset                                                                                                                                                │
│ %cmp2 = icmp eq ptr %m, %g                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ to be optimized to:                                                                                                                                                                       │
│ ```llvm                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ %cmp2 = icmp eq i32 %offset, 0                                                                                                                                                            │
