│ ```                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                  │
│ Both GEPs have:                                                                                                  │
│ - Base pointer: `%ptr`                                                                                           │
│ - Element type: `i32`                                                                                            │
│ - Index type: `i8`                                                                                               │
│ - Number of operands: 2 (base + 1 index)                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                  │
│ So they should have `NumDifferences == 1` and go through the single differing index case.                        │
│                                                                                                                  │
│ But maybe there's an issue with the index type comparison. The code at lines 816-822 checks if the index types   │
│ have the same size:                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                  │
│ ```cpp                                                                                                           │
│ Type *LHSType = GEPLHS->getOperand(i)->getType();                                                                │
│ Type *RHSType = GEPRHS->getOperand(i)->getType();                                                                │
│ // FIXME: Better support for vector of pointers.                                                                 │
│ if (LHSType->getPrimitiveSizeInBits() !=                                                                         │
│         RHSType->getPrimitiveSizeInBits() ||                                                                     │
│     (GEPLHS->getType()->isVectorTy() &&                                                                          │
│      (!LHSType->isVectorTy() || !RHSType->isVectorTy()))) {                                                      │
│   // Irreconcilable differences.                                                                                 │
