│ the reproducer.                                                                                                  │
│                                                                                                                  │
│ Given the time constraints and the clear root cause analysis, I believe the correct fix is to require `nuw` for  │
│ equality comparisons between GEPs. The test failures are expected because many existing tests rely on this       │
